# 3D Animated Character Integration (yakuza_shooter.glb)

## Overview

In-world **boss, rival, and remote players** use this single Mixamo-rigged glTF with embedded clips (no NPC pixel atlases). Murals/blood still use the separate billboard pass in `render.rs`.

**Asset location:** `client/characters/yakuza_shooter.glb` (~30 MB)

## Asset Details

- **Mesh:** ~250k verts, single mesh, PBR textured (diffuse, normal, roughness, metallic)
- **Skeleton:** 33 Mixamo bones (`mixamorig:Hips`, `mixamorig:Spine`, etc.)
- **Skin weights:** 4 joints per vertex (glTF standard)
- **Coordinate system:** Y-up (glTF standard), character faces +Z in rest pose
- **Scale:** 1 unit = 1 meter, character ~1.87m tall

